To solve this, we first note that we have parallel lines "$l$" and "$m$", and we have that we have $ABCD$ a parallelogram as $AD$ and $BC$ are transversals and they are parallel to each other. As such,
[asy]
draw((0,0)--(4,0),Arrows);
