[hide="Answer"]$x=9$[/hide]
```python
# Calculating the value of x based on the given conditions
# The angles 5x - 8 and 143 are supplementary, so their sum is 180 degrees
# Therefore, we set up the equation: 5x - 8 + 143 = 180
# Simplifying the equation: 5x + 135 = 180
# Solving for x: 5x = 180 - 135, 5x = 45, x = 45 / 5, x = 9
x = (180 - 135) / 5
print(x)
